commitResults.messageBody:
* Update user guide

* Update user guide contents to our application

* Add more content to user guide

Previously, the guide has incorrect descriptions of commands.
Lists were also not prefaced by sentences that introduce them.

This commit rectifies incorrect descriptions, based on feedback.
It also adds more sentences to improve readability.

* Update user guide to reflect changes to features

Changes to match, sort, process and done commands were made.

* Add Age Field for Patients

Previously there was:
* no differentiation between the types of Persons
* no differentiation between the types of PersonBuilder
* no change in how different types of Persons are displayed
* no difference in parsing

This commit:
* adds a Patient class which is a Person but with additional criteria
* adds a PatientBuilder class
* different UI displays based on type of Person
* parses Patients and normal Persons differently

* Improve coding style of AddCommandParser.java

* Rectify problems pointed out in PR Review

The following problems are rectified:
* Changed description to 'a valid age'
* Changed condition for a valid age
* Changed MESSAGE_CONSTRAINTS to reflect new conditions
